          "scid": "thig2.4:1.0.3",
          "en": "4. Aḍḍhakāsi"
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig2.4:1.0.4",
          "en": "“No less my fee was than the Kāsī realm Paid in revènue—this was based on that, Value for value,—so the sheriff fixed."
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig2.4:1.0.5",
          "en": "But irksome now is all my loveliness; I weary of it, disillusionized. Ne’er would I more, again and yet again, Run on the round of rebirth and of death! Now real and true for me the Triple Lore. Accomplished is the bidding of the Lord.”"
        }
      ],
